# Telemetry Registry - per-tool telemetry posture
# Format: TELEMETRY_TOOLNAME=STATUS:METHOD
# STATUS values: off (opted out), off_by_design (no telemetry exists), unknown (needs review), on (cannot disable)
# METHOD: how the opt-out is applied or why it's not needed
#
# This file is the documented artifact for PRIV-01.
# Stage 52-tools-privacy.sh reads this file and applies opt-outs (PRIV-02)
# or logs warnings for unknown entries (PRIV-03).

# --- Base System ---
TELEMETRY_BASH=off_by_design:shell_no_telemetry
TELEMETRY_JQ=off_by_design:cli_tools_no_telemetry
TELEMETRY_ADDUSER=off_by_design:system_utility_no_telemetry
